This is a Chat Liyali Zaman Android Application

## Main Features:
- WebView-based chat application
- Loads https://www.chatliyily.com/
- Modern Material Design UI
- High performance optimization
- Ready for Google Play Store

## Files Structure:
- app/src/main/java/ - Source code
- app/src/main/res/ - Resources (layouts, drawables, values)
- app/build.gradle.kts - Build configuration
- AndroidManifest.xml - App manifest

## Build Instructions:
1. Open in Android Studio
2. Sync Gradle files
3. Run Shift+F10 to test
4. For release build: gradlew bundleRelease

## Output:
- Debug APK: app/build/outputs/apk/debug/
- Release AAB: app/build/outputs/bundle/release/app-release.aab

Version: 1.0.0
Target SDK: 34 (Android 14+)
Min SDK: 24 (Android 7.0+)

App is ready to be uploaded to Google Play Console!
